version_description: The best version is not "high quality", so I made one with the correct chords and rythme, as well as the into lick explained.
This version includes chords over every lyric of the song, unlike all other versions.  Version 3 is good but it does not include the end of verse 3 or the bridge.
there are a number of licks not included in previous versions
Additional chords, as Paolo plays it. Neat, concisely formatted. Chord legend included.
